    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>In an older cohort of veterans with a high comorbidity burden, age was the largest predictor of hospitalization, peak disease severity, and mortality. Most infections in six New England states until September, 2020, were from SARS-CoV-2 B.1 lineage, dominated by spike protein D614G substitution in 97.3% of samples.</jats:p>",
